True.  I see bad things done by supposively &quot;good&quot; people all the time (( and not just on Norrath )).  Bad apples are everywhere, and rotten to the core.  In my humble opinion, they should be dragged up before a justice or tribunal and tried for their crimes.  Our family will do that to a family member which has been reported for violating our rules.  We have done just so, and will do so again, if necessary.  Not everyone does this though, but that is their business.<br>
