As I've seen from the other message here, there are those among the Tier'Dal that consider you a &quot;bad apple&quot; too, because you say you're good (or imply, thereof).  That may be true, that you are indeed good.  Would you like to prove this?  I have something for you - we call it &quot;The Test of Evil&quot;.<br>
