Call me a traitor if you please. Call me tainted, cowardly, whelp, etc....take your pick. I know what is right and wrong and you, my friend, do not. That, and only that, is what truly matters to me. Nothing else. I do not require anyone's respect (though it would be nice) nor do I require their love or friendship. I have all I want. Firstly, the chance to stand aside from the insanity of Neriak, and secondly, the chance to sate the hungry spirits of the victims of my kind in their tormentor's blood, if necessary. I require nothing more. As soon as I am proficient enough in combat with this style I will be happy to-no, overjoyed to- fight and defeat the citizenry of my former home. Quite happy, actually. I have my own reasons for hatred of Neriak and I do not require more, though some of the hateful comments here have given me more.<br>
<br>
What hurts me is not the derision of my kin-I can live with that and I in fact welcome it. What hurts is the derision of those who I wanted to be called ally by. Do you hear yourselves? Your spewings of hatred and callings for my blood would do Innoruuk proud! Are your principles universal, or do they only apply to yourselves? Are you hypocrites?! Justice and kindness are ideals that are all-encompassing in scope, they do not merely apply to those whose race or method of combat are those you are comfortable with.<br>
<br>
Before you call yourselves goodly, take a good look at what you say and how you think. I think, unfortunately, that some of you and those that you hate....are more alike then you would wish. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showUserPublicProfile?gid=roninsenshi>RoninSenshi</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Senshi No Adakia<br>Jihad on that ass!</span><br>  Posts: 2142<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(7/30/03 7:37 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4677.topic&index=33>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://members.aol.com/sageofthehalo/Shintou.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Double Standards</span><hr size=1> Nothing speaks louder then anything else.<br>
